	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Springfield <sic>ill</sic></placeName> <date>Jay 26 5626</date></p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Rev Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p rend="align(center)indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
				<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Address</p>
				<p>Care of <persName>Mess Gottlieb &#38; Myers</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Springfield Ill.</placeName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p rend="align(center)">I</p>
				<p>A few weeks ago I have notified you<lb/> that I am here in <placeName>Ka. C.</placeName> and<lb/> I didn&#39;t get an answer from<lb/> you&#44; but I think that the<lb/> letter didn&#39;t reach you<lb/> as it was sent in a private way<lb/> so I am taking the liberty<lb/> to inform you that I am in <placeName>C.</placeName><lb/> Don&#39;t mind me bothering you<lb/> and asking <del>for an</del> to respond<lb/> as I have nobody except you<lb/> and I hope that a similar<lb/> accident wouldn&#39;t happen<lb/> <del>any more</del> again.</p>
				<p>You know that a durable<lb/> hope causes heart disease.<lb/> The Jews here do not have<lb/> any paper may I&#39;ll be able<lb/> to bring <del>it in</del> the &#8220;Occident&#8221;<lb/> I have the pleasure to bring<lb/> my family over here.<lb/> <sic>at</sic> present I am in <placeName>Cleveland</placeName></p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p rend="align(center)">II</p>
				<p><persName>Rev Joseph</persName> and all the<lb/> family feeling fine.</p>
				<p>I hope to get a quick <lb/> answer.<lb/> signing my name below<lb/> I remain devoted to you<lb/> with my heart and soul<lb/> and with sincerity<lb/> and <sic>truthfullness</sic></p>
				<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p><persName>Menachem Elia<add>&#63;</add></persName></p>
				<p><persName role="author">Meyer</persName> <del>Rushbern.</del> <persName role="author">Marcussohn</persName></p>
		</body>
